### ============================================================================
### 🔐 SECCIÓN 1: AUTENTICACIÓN (LLAVES DE ACCESO)
### ============================================================================
### Aquí consigues los Tokens. ¡Haz esto primero!

### 1.1 Login JEFE (ADMIN) - Copia este Token para la Sección 2
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/authenticate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@test.com",
  "password": "admin123"
}

### 1.2 Login EMPLEADO (USER) - Copia este Token para la Sección 3
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/authenticate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "user@test.com",
  "password": "user123"
}

### 1.3 Registro de Usuario Nuevo (Por si quieres crear otro)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nombre": "Nuevo Piloto",
  "email": "nuevo@test.com",
  "password": "123"
}

### ============================================================================
### 👮‍♂️ SECCIÓN 2: GESTIÓN DE RECURSOS (SOLO ADMIN)
### ============================================================================
### Requiere Token de ADMIN (Del paso 1.1)

### 2.1 Crear Recurso (CORREGIDO: Incluye estado y activo para evitar error SQL)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/recursos
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiJ9.eyJzdWIiOiJhZG1pbkB0ZXN0LmNvbSIsImlhdCI6MTc2OTk0MTE2NSwiZXhwIjoxNzcwMDI3NTY1fQ.f4nK9zfSlO6HI95rp2r9hri_mIWl8i6oMXEESlMIT8c

{
  "nombre": "Sala de Juntas Ejecutiva",
  "tipo": "AULA",
  "descripcion": "Sala con proyector 4K",
  "codigoQr": "SALA-VIP-01",
  "estado": "DISPONIBLE",
  "activo": true
}

### 2.2 Borrar Recurso (Admin)
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/recursos/1
Authorization: Bearer PEGA_AQUI_TOKEN_ADMIN


### ============================================================================
### 👤 SECCIÓN 3: ZONA DE USUARIOS Y RESERVAS
### ============================================================================
### Requiere Token de USER (Del paso 1.2) o ADMIN

### 3.1 Listar Recursos (Público - Todos pueden ver)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/recursos
Authorization: Bearer PEGA_AQUI_TOKEN_CUALQUIERA

### 3.2 Crear Reserva "Mágica" (Sin enviar ID de usuario)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/reservas
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiJ9.eyJzdWIiOiJ1c2VyQHRlc3QuY29tIiwiaWF0IjoxNzY5OTQxMjE1LCJleHAiOjE3NzAwMjc2MTV9.jVuoBWl-W9BoFCGX1kisunzdSZoXuOZji_NqLy-R98o

{
  "fechaInicio": "2026-02-20T10:00:00",
  "fechaFin": "2026-02-20T12:00:00",
  "recurso": { "id": 1 }
}

### 3.3 Ver Reservas
GET http://localhost:8080/api/reservas
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiJ9.eyJzdWIiOiJ1c2VyQHRlc3QuY29tIiwiaWF0IjoxNzY5OTQxMjE1LCJleHAiOjE3NzAwMjc2MTV9.jVuoBWl-W9BoFCGX1kisunzdSZoXuOZji_NqLy-R98o

### ============================================================================
### 🛡️ SECCIÓN 4: PRUEBAS DE SEGURIDAD (HACKING)
### ============================================================================

### 4.1 Intento de Usuario Normal creando Recurso (DEBE FALLAR - 403 Forbidden)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/recursos
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer PEGA_AQUI_TOKEN_USER

{
  "nombre": "Intento Hackeo",
  "tipo": "AULA",
  "estado": "DISPONIBLE",
  "activo": true
}

### 4.2 Intento de Acceso sin Token (DEBE FALLAR - 403 Forbidden)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/recursos

### ============================================================================
### ⚠️ SECCIÓN 5: ERRORES DE LÓGICA (VALIDACIONES)
### ============================================================================

### 5.1 Fechas Imposibles (Fin antes de Inicio)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/reservas
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer PEGA_AQUI_TOKEN_USER

{
  "fechaInicio": "2026-02-10T12:00:00",
  "fechaFin": "2026-02-10T10:00:00",
  "usuario": { "id": 2 },
  "recurso": { "id": 1 }
}

### 5.2 Solapamiento (Conflicto de horario con la reserva 3.2)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/reservas
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer PEGA_AQUI_TOKEN_USER

{
  "fechaInicio": "2026-02-10T11:00:00",
  "fechaFin": "2026-02-10T13:00:00",
  "usuario": { "id": 2 },
  "recurso": { "id": 1 }
}

### ============================================================================
### 🛠️ SECCIÓN EXTRA: GESTIÓN DE USUARIOS (CRUD)
### ============================================================================

### 6.1 Ver usuarios
GET http://localhost:8080/api/usuarios
Authorization: Bearer PEGA_AQUI_TOKEN_ADMIN

### 6.2 Actualizar usuario
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/usuarios/2
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer PEGA_AQUI_TOKEN_ADMIN

{
  "nombre": "Pepe Renombrado",
  "email": "pepe@test.com"
}

